Text.SourceString: Ommmmm…//Oh. A new face. Feeling really good vibes from you, mate.
Text.LocalizedString: Ommmmm…//Oh. A new face. Feeling really good vibes from you, mate.

Text.SourceString: May our paths cross again.
Text.LocalizedString: May our paths cross again.

Text.SourceString: I sell a little bit of everything. Some stuff's rare, my friend.//I don't exactly specialize, you know?
Text.LocalizedString: I sell a little bit of everything. Some stuff's rare, my friend.//I don't exactly specialize, you know?

Text.SourceString: My inventory's kind of...eclectic, I guess?//<portrait=happy>Something like that.
Text.LocalizedString: My inventory's kind of...eclectic, I guess?//<portrait=happy>Something like that.

Text.SourceString: If you need rare seeds, rare furniture, or something specific, I might be your guy.//I might have it somewhere in my caravan.
Text.LocalizedString: If you need rare seeds, rare furniture, or something specific, I might be your guy.//I might have it somewhere in my caravan.

Text.SourceString: I’ll definitely sell it to you if I can find it. Check often!
Text.LocalizedString: I’ll definitely sell it to you if I can find it. Check often!

Text.SourceString: This island is breathtaking.
Text.LocalizedString: This island is breathtaking.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes we need to just chill and take in the vibes around us.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes we need to just chill and take in the vibes around us.

Text.SourceString: You don’t need a lot of money to be happy, <PlayerName>$player</>.
Text.LocalizedString: You don’t need a lot of money to be happy, <PlayerName>$player</>.

Text.SourceString: Look at me. I don’t have a lot of money, but I’m happy.//<portrait=happy>I’ve got all I need.
Text.LocalizedString: Look at me. I don’t have a lot of money, but I’m happy.//<portrait=happy>I’ve got all I need.

Text.SourceString: People toss away the coolest things, it's a total bummer.//I like to give those things a new home.
Text.LocalizedString: People toss away the coolest things, it's a total bummer.//I like to give those things a new home.

Text.SourceString: Yeah, I sell them, sure. But it's all about recycling, my friend.//You got the idea. Right on!
Text.LocalizedString: Yeah, I sell them, sure. But it's all about recycling, my friend.//You got the idea. Right on!

Text.SourceString: Umm, are you a folk type of person? Or more of a mate type?
Text.LocalizedString: Umm, are you a folk type of person? Or more of a mate type?

Text.SourceString: No need to be so confused, my friend. It’s a hard one.//<portrait=normal>Identity is never easy to pin down.
Text.LocalizedString: No need to be so confused, my friend. It’s a hard one.//<portrait=normal>Identity is never easy to pin down.

Text.SourceString: I run errands for <NpcName>Sam</> sometimes.//Little things like grabbing seeds. He hooks me up with a sweet deal for the trouble.
Text.LocalizedString: I run errands for <NpcName>Sam</> sometimes.//Little things like grabbing seeds. He hooks me up with a sweet deal for the trouble.

Text.SourceString: The beach is the ultimate chill spot.//<portrait=happy>Between the waves, the birds...your mind just empties out.
Text.LocalizedString: The beach is the ultimate chill spot.//<portrait=happy>Between the waves, the birds...your mind just empties out.

Text.SourceString: Not even room to think, honestly. Sometimes, I find myself sitting at the beach, and…//<portrait=surprised><Italic>Bam!</> Suddenly it’s nighttime.
Text.LocalizedString: Not even room to think, honestly. Sometimes, I find myself sitting at the beach, and…//<portrait=surprised><Italic>Bam!</> Suddenly it’s nighttime.

Text.SourceString: I like to plant some flowers around the van sometimes, you know, to help the bees.//I'll sell a few too.
Text.LocalizedString: I like to plant some flowers around the van sometimes, you know, to help the bees.//I'll sell a few too.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes I grow herbs, but not always.//<portrait=normal>I don't buy seeds, I just plant whatever I find around the island.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes I grow herbs, but not always.//<portrait=normal>I don't buy seeds, I just plant whatever I find around the island.

Text.SourceString: On weekends, I'm usually kicking back in the van.//Tidying up.
Text.LocalizedString: On weekends, I'm usually kicking back in the van.//Tidying up.

Text.SourceString: Um, cleaning up stuff. You know. This and that.//<portrait=annoyed>There’s a lot to clean.
Text.LocalizedString: Um, cleaning up stuff. You know. This and that.//<portrait=annoyed>There’s a lot to clean.

Text.SourceString: Ah, <PlayerName>$player</>, <PlayerName>$player</>. Here I am… And there you are…
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, <PlayerName>$player</>, <PlayerName>$player</>. Here I am… And there you are…

Text.SourceString: I’ve been wandering around, wondering to myself…//<portrait=happy>“Who am I destined to meet on this joyful day?”
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve been wandering around, wondering to myself…//<portrait=happy>“Who am I destined to meet on this joyful day?”

Text.SourceString: I’m a wanderer. I don’t settle in one spot.//It’s just not who I am.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m a wanderer. I don’t settle in one spot.//It’s just not who I am.

Text.SourceString: Yes, I’ve always been a wanderer.//<portrait=normal>Since the age of three, according to my mom.
Text.LocalizedString: Yes, I’ve always been a wanderer.//<portrait=normal>Since the age of three, according to my mom.

Text.SourceString: I’ve tried boots before. But they just didn’t feel right on my feet.
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve tried boots before. But they just didn’t feel right on my feet.

Text.SourceString: Also, there was this strong odor after wearing them awhile.//<portrait=happy>I took that as my feet telling me no.
Text.LocalizedString: Also, there was this strong odor after wearing them awhile.//<portrait=happy>I took that as my feet telling me no.

Text.SourceString: Yeah, the van works.//Well, the brakes are a little funny sometimes.//<portrait=happy>You gotta stand on them pretty hard, but hey! Aside from that, it rides okay.
Text.LocalizedString: Yeah, the van works.//Well, the brakes are a little funny sometimes.//<portrait=happy>You gotta stand on them pretty hard, but hey! Aside from that, it rides okay.

Text.SourceString: Oh, Tuesday, Tuesday. Tomorrow is probably Wednesday.//<portrait=concerned>It’s all <Italic>so</> predictable. This world needs a shake-up and a jolt of creativity.//<portrait=happy>And you know what? Yesterday was indeed Monday.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, Tuesday, Tuesday. Tomorrow is probably Wednesday.//<portrait=concerned>It’s all <Italic>so</> predictable. This world needs a shake-up and a jolt of creativity.//<portrait=happy>And you know what? Yesterday was indeed Monday.

Text.SourceString: I like to think it was meant to be Moon Day. The day of brightness.//<portrait=happy>It’s the beginning of the week, which means it’s the day of rejoicing…//Are we getting each other here?
Text.LocalizedString: I like to think it was meant to be Moon Day. The day of brightness.//<portrait=happy>It’s the beginning of the week, which means it’s the day of rejoicing…//Are we getting each other here?

Text.SourceString: There are a lot of things you can pick up at the beach.
Text.LocalizedString: There are a lot of things you can pick up at the beach.

Text.SourceString: Coconuts, seashells, shiny ones, not-so-shiny ones... Endless possibilities, <PlayerName>$Player</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Coconuts, seashells, shiny ones, not-so-shiny ones... Endless possibilities, <PlayerName>$Player</>.

Text.SourceString: I think about my duck sometimes…//<portrait=happy>What’s going through his mind and all that.//You know, the usual.
Text.LocalizedString: I think about my duck sometimes…//<portrait=happy>What’s going through his mind and all that.//You know, the usual.

Text.SourceString: I got a duck from <NpcName>Jack</>, but he’s boarding him for me.//<portrait=normal>I think it’s better for Funbucket to live with his friends than to travel with me. You know…
Text.LocalizedString: I got a duck from <NpcName>Jack</>, but he’s boarding him for me.//<portrait=normal>I think it’s better for Funbucket to live with his friends than to travel with me. You know…

Text.SourceString: Funbucket is one happy fella.//<portrait=normal>I was gathering fodder for <NpcName>Jack</> when I first saw him running around the yard.
Text.LocalizedString: Funbucket is one happy fella.//<portrait=normal>I was gathering fodder for <NpcName>Jack</> when I first saw him running around the yard.

Text.SourceString: When my store is quiet like this, I think about my duck sometimes.//He lives at the barn over there.
Text.LocalizedString: When my store is quiet like this, I think about my duck sometimes.//He lives at the barn over there.

Text.SourceString: You give off a real animal-loving vibe.
Text.LocalizedString: You give off a real animal-loving vibe.

Text.SourceString: Sandals are the way to go. I’m a no-cage kind of guy.//Not for animals, not for my feet.
Text.LocalizedString: Sandals are the way to go. I’m a no-cage kind of guy.//Not for animals, not for my feet.

Text.SourceString: You know what I’m saying, <PlayerName>$player</>?//<portrait=happy>Whenever I want, I’m free to see my toes dancing. Now, that’s something.
Text.LocalizedString: You know what I’m saying, <PlayerName>$player</>?//<portrait=happy>Whenever I want, I’m free to see my toes dancing. Now, that’s something.

Text.SourceString: I’m a wanderer. I don’t settle in one spot. It’s just not who I am.//<portrait=annoyed>Except for today, I guess.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m a wanderer. I don’t settle in one spot. It’s just not who I am.//<portrait=annoyed>Except for today, I guess.

Text.SourceString: Trees are amazing. They just do their thing, and they don't judge...
Text.LocalizedString: Trees are amazing. They just do their thing, and they don't judge...

Text.SourceString: Sure, they can't talk, but that's beside the point.//The real point is us, <PlayerName>$player</>. We've got all this knowledge, but sometimes we use it to judge each other.
Text.LocalizedString: Sure, they can't talk, but that's beside the point.//The real point is us, <PlayerName>$player</>. We've got all this knowledge, but sometimes we use it to judge each other.

Text.SourceString: My coffee? Yeah, I had it this morning. Why?
Text.LocalizedString: My coffee? Yeah, I had it this morning. Why?

Text.SourceString: Sometimes I swing by the ranch to help out with the animals.//Plus, <NpcName>Jack</> hooks me up with a part-time gig gathering feed.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes I swing by the ranch to help out with the animals.//Plus, <NpcName>Jack</> hooks me up with a part-time gig gathering feed.

Text.SourceString: It's easy work, and the extra cash doesn't hurt.
Text.LocalizedString: It's easy work, and the extra cash doesn't hurt.

Text.SourceString: My friend! <PlayerName>$player</>! How are we doing today? The weather is kind to me today, my friend.//I couldn’t ask for a better Thursday.
Text.LocalizedString: My friend! <PlayerName>$player</>! How are we doing today? The weather is kind to me today, my friend.//I couldn’t ask for a better Thursday.

Text.SourceString: I could try, though. But I’m sure I’d fail.
Text.LocalizedString: I could try, though. But I’m sure I’d fail.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes time goes fast, and sometimes it goes really slow. Like really, really slow…
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes time goes fast, and sometimes it goes really slow. Like really, really slow…

Text.SourceString: This time thing isn’t for me, my friend. I learned early in life that I’m cruising at a different altitude.
Text.LocalizedString: This time thing isn’t for me, my friend. I learned early in life that I’m cruising at a different altitude.

Text.SourceString: I’ve been trying to pick up a new hobby lately. I do carpentry, but not too often. What do you like to do in your free time, <NPCName>Luke</>?
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve been trying to pick up a new hobby lately. I do carpentry, but not too often. What do you like to do in your free time, <NPCName>Luke</>?

Text.SourceString: Errr… Sorry. This is awkward.//<portrait=happy>Names are all jumbled up. Way too many people here to remember… <PlayerName>$player</>, <PlayerName>$player</>, <PlayerName>$player</>…
Text.LocalizedString: Errr… Sorry. This is awkward.//<portrait=happy>Names are all jumbled up. Way too many people here to remember… <PlayerName>$player</>, <PlayerName>$player</>, <PlayerName>$player</>…

Text.SourceString: Visiting the cavern, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Visiting the cavern, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: I’d be careful in there if I were you. I took my quartz inside the cavern one time. You know, to recharge the vibe.//And I came out with a couple of bats in my hair. Nesting.
Text.LocalizedString: I’d be careful in there if I were you. I took my quartz inside the cavern one time. You know, to recharge the vibe.//And I came out with a couple of bats in my hair. Nesting.

Text.SourceString: You heard of this thing? Um…tempeh?//<portrait=happy>Oh yeah… That stuff is yummy as heck. Nothing beats fresh bananas, though.
Text.LocalizedString: You heard of this thing? Um…tempeh?//<portrait=happy>Oh yeah… That stuff is yummy as heck. Nothing beats fresh bananas, though.

Text.SourceString: I’m gonna take a chill day today, <PlayerName>$player</>. See if I can make some money here instead.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m gonna take a chill day today, <PlayerName>$player</>. See if I can make some money here instead.

Text.SourceString: My friend! <PlayerName>$player</>! How are we doing today?//The bees are kind to me today, my friend. I couldn’t ask for a better Sunday.
Text.LocalizedString: My friend! <PlayerName>$player</>! How are we doing today?//The bees are kind to me today, my friend. I couldn’t ask for a better Sunday.

Text.SourceString: I could try, though. But I’m sure I’d fail.
Text.LocalizedString: I could try, though. But I’m sure I’d fail.

Text.SourceString: Happy New Year!
Text.LocalizedString: Happy New Year!

Text.SourceString: You got a trumpet to blow there, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: You got a trumpet to blow there, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: Lots of mushrooms grow on this island, mate.//Hmm. Hang on… Let me list them for you! Shiitake, black trumpet, truffle…
Text.LocalizedString: Lots of mushrooms grow on this island, mate.//Hmm. Hang on… Let me list them for you! Shiitake, black trumpet, truffle…

Text.SourceString: There’s that tiny red one, the poisonous kind.//<portrait=normal>You probably shouldn’t eat it, though…//<portrait=happy>Just to be safe, if you find any, give them to me.
Text.LocalizedString: There’s that tiny red one, the poisonous kind.//<portrait=normal>You probably shouldn’t eat it, though…//<portrait=happy>Just to be safe, if you find any, give them to me.

Text.SourceString: You seem like the chill farmer type. Not the get-off-my-lawn kind.//<portrait=normal>Know what I mean?//<portrait=concerned>A friend was camping on somebody’s lawn one time, and he may have been kicked out.
Text.LocalizedString: You seem like the chill farmer type. Not the get-off-my-lawn kind.//<portrait=normal>Know what I mean?//<portrait=concerned>A friend was camping on somebody’s lawn one time, and he may have been kicked out.

Text.SourceString: Fine, fine. Who am I kidding? It was me. I was the <Italic>friend</> who got kicked out.//<portrait=normal>In my defense, it looked like an overgrown cemetery.
Text.LocalizedString: Fine, fine. Who am I kidding? It was me. I was the <Italic>friend</> who got kicked out.//<portrait=normal>In my defense, it looked like an overgrown cemetery.

Text.SourceString: What are you planting on your farm, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: What are you planting on your farm, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: Been a long day, hasn't it?//<portrait=annoyed>You look kinda wiped.
Text.LocalizedString: Been a long day, hasn't it?//<portrait=annoyed>You look kinda wiped.

Text.SourceString: If I were you, I'd kick back and surround myself with some good energy quartz.//<portrait=happy>Just breathe in the good vibes till you're buzzing with joy.
Text.LocalizedString: If I were you, I'd kick back and surround myself with some good energy quartz.//<portrait=happy>Just breathe in the good vibes till you're buzzing with joy.

Text.SourceString: <PlayerName>$player</>, don’t you just love all the flowers? So much life around us. Let’s stay still for a moment and absorb it all.//<portrait=surprised><Italic>Ommmmm!</>
Text.LocalizedString: <PlayerName>$player</>, don’t you just love all the flowers? So much life around us. Let’s stay still for a moment and absorb it all.//<portrait=surprised><Italic>Ommmmm!</>

Text.SourceString: I love Spring. I can hear the birds chirping again.//<portrait=happy>Like me! I’m <Italic>chirping</> again. <Italic>I’m a bird!</>
Text.LocalizedString: I love Spring. I can hear the birds chirping again.//<portrait=happy>Like me! I’m <Italic>chirping</> again. <Italic>I’m a bird!</>

Text.SourceString: Do you have any of those fancy-schmancy mushroom logs, <PlayerName>$player</>?//They’re pretty cool, but I like to gather mushrooms in the wild. There are plenty around the island right now.
Text.LocalizedString: Do you have any of those fancy-schmancy mushroom logs, <PlayerName>$player</>?//They’re pretty cool, but I like to gather mushrooms in the wild. There are plenty around the island right now.

Text.SourceString: Are you allergic to pollen, mate? The doc's been sneezing like mad. I feel for him.//<portrait=normal>The one with the short hair, not the one with the sick green hair.
Text.LocalizedString: Are you allergic to pollen, mate? The doc's been sneezing like mad. I feel for him.//<portrait=normal>The one with the short hair, not the one with the sick green hair.

Text.SourceString: Ah, Spring. Everything is just so beautiful, isn’t it?
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, Spring. Everything is just so beautiful, isn’t it?

Text.SourceString: Spring mushrooms taste different from Fall mushrooms.//Both are delicious, though.
Text.LocalizedString: Spring mushrooms taste different from Fall mushrooms.//Both are delicious, though.

Text.SourceString: Ah, Summer. Enjoy the heat and humidity, <PlayerName>$player</>. I feel great.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, Summer. Enjoy the heat and humidity, <PlayerName>$player</>. I feel great.

Text.SourceString: I hear people complaining about the heat, but nah, mate. Just enjoy it.//Soak up all that sunshine.
Text.LocalizedString: I hear people complaining about the heat, but nah, mate. Just enjoy it.//Soak up all that sunshine.

Text.SourceString: Summer's just more of the same good vibes for me. Super chill.//Well, super hot, actually, but you get it.
Text.LocalizedString: Summer's just more of the same good vibes for me. Super chill.//Well, super hot, actually, but you get it.

Text.SourceString: Whoo! It’s getting hot, isn’t it? But no sweat. We just gotta take more showers, eh?//<portrait=happy>See what I did there? No sweat?
Text.LocalizedString: Whoo! It’s getting hot, isn’t it? But no sweat. We just gotta take more showers, eh?//<portrait=happy>See what I did there? No sweat?

Text.SourceString: Sometimes the van heats up like an oven, but then I can just roll over to the Tavern or chill in front of <NPCName>Sam’s</> fresh groceries to cool down.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes the van heats up like an oven, but then I can just roll over to the Tavern or chill in front of <NPCName>Sam’s</> fresh groceries to cool down.

Text.SourceString: You hear that Summer music, <PlayerName>$player</>? Pretty awesome, isn’t it?//<portrait=happy>You have to feel it in your heart. Open your third ear… Then you can hear… Is that an angklung?
Text.LocalizedString: You hear that Summer music, <PlayerName>$player</>? Pretty awesome, isn’t it?//<portrait=happy>You have to feel it in your heart. Open your third ear… Then you can hear… Is that an angklung?

Text.SourceString: It’s all right that the grass is a bit patchy, you know? Sometimes nature just needs to do its thing.//Doesn’t mean it’s less great.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s all right that the grass is a bit patchy, you know? Sometimes nature just needs to do its thing.//Doesn’t mean it’s less great.

Text.SourceString: Am I sad the leaves are falling?//A little bit, but I know they’ll grow back.
Text.LocalizedString: Am I sad the leaves are falling?//A little bit, but I know they’ll grow back.

Text.SourceString: Take a deep breath, <PlayerName>$player</>. In…and out… Fill your lungs with that crisp Fall air. Nice, right?
Text.LocalizedString: Take a deep breath, <PlayerName>$player</>. In…and out… Fill your lungs with that crisp Fall air. Nice, right?

Text.SourceString: The Fall breeze always gets me itching to hit the road.
Text.LocalizedString: The Fall breeze always gets me itching to hit the road.

Text.SourceString: See the red and orange on the leaves? It's my cue to roll out.//<portrait=happy>Don’t worry, mate, I’m coming back. So don’t miss me too much.
Text.LocalizedString: See the red and orange on the leaves? It's my cue to roll out.//<portrait=happy>Don’t worry, mate, I’m coming back. So don’t miss me too much.

Text.SourceString: Ah, too bad I’m leaving soon.//I see all these mushrooms popping up, and I won’t be able to gather any on my trip.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, too bad I’m leaving soon.//I see all these mushrooms popping up, and I won’t be able to gather any on my trip.

Text.SourceString: Better start getting ready for my trip next week.//<portrait=normal>Let’s see, I need to stock up on mushrooms, green tea…
Text.LocalizedString: Better start getting ready for my trip next week.//<portrait=normal>Let’s see, I need to stock up on mushrooms, green tea…

Text.SourceString: My trip was epic, <PlayerName>$player</>. That's the perk of van life... My home is always where I park it!//<portrait=normal>Now, I'm all set to chill here for a while.
Text.LocalizedString: My trip was epic, <PlayerName>$player</>. That's the perk of van life... My home is always where I park it!//<portrait=normal>Now, I'm all set to chill here for a while.

Text.SourceString: <PlayerName>$player</>, let’s take a deep breath of that chilly Winter.//<portrait=surprised>Whoa… That is <Italic>cold!</>//<portrait=blushing>I think my brain froze a little there.
Text.LocalizedString: <PlayerName>$player</>, let’s take a deep breath of that chilly Winter.//<portrait=surprised>Whoa… That is <Italic>cold!</>//<portrait=blushing>I think my brain froze a little there.

Text.SourceString: What’s the point of complaining about the cold air? It is what it is, <PlayerName>$player</>.//Besides, look at all that beautiful snow.
Text.LocalizedString: What’s the point of complaining about the cold air? It is what it is, <PlayerName>$player</>.//Besides, look at all that beautiful snow.

Text.SourceString: It’s kinda chilly, you know? Maybe I’ll head to the Tavern to warm up before I go to bed.//<portrait=normal>This whole town is my home, mate. The Tavern, this van…your cabin, eh? Heh heh heh!
Text.LocalizedString: It’s kinda chilly, you know? Maybe I’ll head to the Tavern to warm up before I go to bed.//<portrait=normal>This whole town is my home, mate. The Tavern, this van…your cabin, eh? Heh heh heh!

Text.SourceString: You know, once I’m all snuggled up in bed, I barely notice how cold it is.//It’s kinda nice, actually, to sleep when it’s freezing cold out. As long as I don’t freeze, that’s all I ask.
Text.LocalizedString: You know, once I’m all snuggled up in bed, I barely notice how cold it is.//It’s kinda nice, actually, to sleep when it’s freezing cold out. As long as I don’t freeze, that’s all I ask.

Text.SourceString: All the snow on the ground… That’s Winter, mate.//It’s one of the reasons I always come back here for Winter. Who wants to miss out on this beauty?//But also, I don’t have a long-term parking permit anywhere else.
Text.LocalizedString: All the snow on the ground… That’s Winter, mate.//It’s one of the reasons I always come back here for Winter. Who wants to miss out on this beauty?//But also, I don’t have a long-term parking permit anywhere else.

Text.SourceString: Got a few new things for sale. Swing by and check it out?
Text.LocalizedString: Got a few new things for sale. Swing by and check it out?

Text.SourceString: Picked up some neat stuff on my trip.
Text.LocalizedString: Picked up some neat stuff on my trip.

Text.SourceString: My hair? It's all natural, mate. Just letting it do its thing.
Text.LocalizedString: My hair? It's all natural, mate. Just letting it do its thing.

Text.SourceString: If it wants to lay flat, it'll do so like a champ.//If it wants to float in the humidity, who are we to stop it?
Text.LocalizedString: If it wants to lay flat, it'll do so like a champ.//If it wants to float in the humidity, who are we to stop it?

Text.SourceString: Sandals are the way to go. I’m a no-cage kind of guy. Not for animals, not for my feet.
Text.LocalizedString: Sandals are the way to go. I’m a no-cage kind of guy. Not for animals, not for my feet.

Text.SourceString: You know what I’m saying, <PlayerName>$player</>? I’m free to see my toes dancing whenever I want.
Text.LocalizedString: You know what I’m saying, <PlayerName>$player</>? I’m free to see my toes dancing whenever I want.

Text.SourceString: Aaaaah… Say it with me. <Italic>Aaaaah!</>
Text.LocalizedString: Aaaaah… Say it with me. <Italic>Aaaaah!</>

Text.SourceString: I bet you’re feeling better already.//<portrait=normal>It exercises your esophagus. It’s all dancing in there, <PlayerName>$Player</>. Happy, dancing muscles.
Text.LocalizedString: I bet you’re feeling better already.//<portrait=normal>It exercises your esophagus. It’s all dancing in there, <PlayerName>$Player</>. Happy, dancing muscles.

Text.SourceString: I’m heading out about two weeks from now. Need a change of scenery, you know?
Text.LocalizedString: I’m heading out about two weeks from now. Need a change of scenery, you know?

Text.SourceString: I'll catch you in the Winter, and I'll bring a stash of cool stuff to trade.
Text.LocalizedString: I'll catch you in the Winter, and I'll bring a stash of cool stuff to trade.

Text.SourceString: Nice to see you again, <PlayerName>$player</>!
Text.LocalizedString: Nice to see you again, <PlayerName>$player</>!

Text.SourceString: Great to be back. I should go to see <NpcName>Suki</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Great to be back. I should go to see <NpcName>Suki</>.

Text.SourceString: Ah… Yeah, and other people too.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah… Yeah, and other people too.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Luke</> showed me a picture of Funbucket at the Animal Festival, and he looked like he was having the time of his life.//He just walked and walked, saying hi to everybody. A kind-hearted fellow, that one.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Luke</> showed me a picture of Funbucket at the Animal Festival, and he looked like he was having the time of his life.//He just walked and walked, saying hi to everybody. A kind-hearted fellow, that one.

Text.SourceString: Funbucket is my boy!
Text.LocalizedString: Funbucket is my boy!

Text.SourceString: Score any truffles today? I scoped out the area this morning and only scored a few.
Text.LocalizedString: Score any truffles today? I scoped out the area this morning and only scored a few.

Text.SourceString: Around this time, there should be plenty across the island.
Text.LocalizedString: Around this time, there should be plenty across the island.

Text.SourceString: I’m not feeling too jolly today.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m not feeling too jolly today.

Text.SourceString: Got the blues, I think… Hmm…
Text.LocalizedString: Got the blues, I think… Hmm…

Text.SourceString: The van's pretty toasty. I've got this little stove that doubles as a heater.
Text.LocalizedString: The van's pretty toasty. I've got this little stove that doubles as a heater.

Text.SourceString: The space isn’t that big, so it doesn’t take much to heat it up.//<portrait=normal>But if I get too cold, I walk over to the Tavern and chill the night away.
Text.LocalizedString: The space isn’t that big, so it doesn’t take much to heat it up.//<portrait=normal>But if I get too cold, I walk over to the Tavern and chill the night away.

Text.SourceString: A ton of rain coming down lately…
Text.LocalizedString: A ton of rain coming down lately…

Text.SourceString: It’s much warmer here when it rains than it is in my caravan.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s much warmer here when it rains than it is in my caravan.

Text.SourceString: It isn’t too bad here during the rain, eh?
Text.LocalizedString: It isn’t too bad here during the rain, eh?

Text.SourceString: I should go back. I’m so sleepy!
Text.LocalizedString: I should go back. I’m so sleepy!

Text.SourceString: Why is it raining so hard lately? Jeez…
Text.LocalizedString: Why is it raining so hard lately? Jeez…

Text.SourceString: *mumbling to himself* Is there a leak in my caravan?
Text.LocalizedString: *mumbling to himself* Is there a leak in my caravan?

Text.SourceString: It’s much warmer here when it rains than it is in my caravan.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s much warmer here when it rains than it is in my caravan.

Text.SourceString: It’s much warmer here when it rains than it is in my caravan.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s much warmer here when it rains than it is in my caravan.

Text.SourceString: A beanie sure helps when it’s snowing.
Text.LocalizedString: A beanie sure helps when it’s snowing.

Text.SourceString: It’s a nice change to come here after being at a music festival in the hot desert.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s a nice change to come here after being at a music festival in the hot desert.

Text.SourceString: I think I’m just gonna chill here today.
Text.LocalizedString: I think I’m just gonna chill here today.

Text.SourceString: I can sell you my crystals to give you some extra good vibes in your cabin.//Just offer me the right price…//<portrait=happy>If the crystals are feeling it, they’re all yours.
Text.LocalizedString: I can sell you my crystals to give you some extra good vibes in your cabin.//Just offer me the right price…//<portrait=happy>If the crystals are feeling it, they’re all yours.

Text.SourceString: The stars are watching us down here, <PlayerName>$player</>.//They’re writing us letters, stories that we can only read in our dreams.
Text.LocalizedString: The stars are watching us down here, <PlayerName>$player</>.//They’re writing us letters, stories that we can only read in our dreams.

Text.SourceString: All I need in life is green tea and bananas.//<portrait=happy>They’re all I need to spread positivity.
Text.LocalizedString: All I need in life is green tea and bananas.//<portrait=happy>They’re all I need to spread positivity.

Text.SourceString: Rose quartz gives all the love…//<portrait=normal>We get love. We give love. You know what I mean…
Text.LocalizedString: Rose quartz gives all the love…//<portrait=normal>We get love. We give love. You know what I mean…

Text.SourceString: It isn’t too bad living in this thing.//<portrait=happy>The best part is you can always drive off when you’re bored. Ha!
Text.LocalizedString: It isn’t too bad living in this thing.//<portrait=happy>The best part is you can always drive off when you’re bored. Ha!

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Suki</> taught me how to make green smoothies.//<portrait=annoyed>Want one?
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Suki</> taught me how to make green smoothies.//<portrait=annoyed>Want one?

Text.SourceString: Welcome to my crib!
Text.LocalizedString: Welcome to my crib!

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Emily</> cuts my hair. She oozes talent, doesn’t she?//But that’s not why I’m here.//I’m here to deliver some stuff for <NpcName>Sam</>.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Emily</> cuts my hair. She oozes talent, doesn’t she?//But that’s not why I’m here.//I’m here to deliver some stuff for <NpcName>Sam</>.

Text.SourceString: Hmm… I thought about settling down and opening a store like this.//<portrait=concerned>But between you and me, it isn’t really my style.
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm… I thought about settling down and opening a store like this.//<portrait=concerned>But between you and me, it isn’t really my style.

Text.SourceString: Dry rice can last four to five years, and it’s filling.//So I try to keep a couple boxes in my van.
Text.LocalizedString: Dry rice can last four to five years, and it’s filling.//So I try to keep a couple boxes in my van.

Text.SourceString: Hmm… Should I buy bread or tortillas?
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm… Should I buy bread or tortillas?

Text.SourceString: It’s quite a walk to get here, eh? Especially from your place.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s quite a walk to get here, eh? Especially from your place.

Text.SourceString: One of these days, I’m going to start writing about crystals.
Text.LocalizedString: One of these days, I’m going to start writing about crystals.

Text.SourceString: You can mark my word on that! I think it’s about time. You know what I mean?
Text.LocalizedString: You can mark my word on that! I think it’s about time. You know what I mean?

Text.SourceString: I wanted to park here, but Mayor <NpcName>Connor</> never issued me a permit. Ha!
Text.LocalizedString: I wanted to park here, but Mayor <NpcName>Connor</> never issued me a permit. Ha!

Text.SourceString: He was concerned my van might wreck the festival grounds.//<portrait=normal>I understand. All cool.
Text.LocalizedString: He was concerned my van might wreck the festival grounds.//<portrait=normal>I understand. All cool.

Text.SourceString: I’m saving all these wild fruits for my lunch tomorrow.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m saving all these wild fruits for my lunch tomorrow.

Text.SourceString: There might still be some near the inn! Go, grab ’em!
Text.LocalizedString: There might still be some near the inn! Go, grab ’em!

Text.SourceString: I heard this area isn’t on the original map of the town. The locals built it up years ago because they needed higher ground for the lighthouse.
Text.LocalizedString: I heard this area isn’t on the original map of the town. The locals built it up years ago because they needed higher ground for the lighthouse.

Text.SourceString: Would you believe me if I told you I learned that in my dreams?
Text.LocalizedString: Would you believe me if I told you I learned that in my dreams?

Text.SourceString: Well, well, well. Look who’s here.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, well, well. Look who’s here.

Text.SourceString: Getting away from town, huh? You and me both.//What a view.
Text.LocalizedString: Getting away from town, huh? You and me both.//What a view.

Text.SourceString: I like to meditate here. I think it might be my favorite spot. It’s a bit out of the way.//Just me and the ocean waves.
Text.LocalizedString: I like to meditate here. I think it might be my favorite spot. It’s a bit out of the way.//Just me and the ocean waves.

Text.SourceString: Being around animals makes me happy – especially this cute little duck.
Text.LocalizedString: Being around animals makes me happy – especially this cute little duck.

Text.SourceString: Funbucket is one happy fella.
Text.LocalizedString: Funbucket is one happy fella.

Text.SourceString: I’m picking up a bit of work, mate. <NpcName>Jack</> hires me part-time to check in on the animals.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m picking up a bit of work, mate. <NpcName>Jack</> hires me part-time to check in on the animals.

Text.SourceString: It’s a breeze.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s a breeze.

Text.SourceString: You ever feel like you cough so hard that part of your lung falls out?
Text.LocalizedString: You ever feel like you cough so hard that part of your lung falls out?

Text.SourceString: Oh, okay. It’s just me then. Hmm…
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, okay. It’s just me then. Hmm…

Text.SourceString: Whoopsie!//Watch your step there! <portrait=concerned>You almost got my foot <Italic>again</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Whoopsie!//Watch your step there! <portrait=concerned>You almost got my foot <Italic>again</>.

Text.SourceString: You can only buy things from the window. Sorry, friend. It’s nothing personal – just a business decision.
Text.LocalizedString: You can only buy things from the window. Sorry, friend. It’s nothing personal – just a business decision.

Text.SourceString: I don’t know what to tell you. It’s accounting.//<portrait=normal>Separating accounts in sole proprietorship to develop integrity and strength of my personal brand.//It’s true! Look it up in the library or something.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t know what to tell you. It’s accounting.//<portrait=normal>Separating accounts in sole proprietorship to develop integrity and strength of my personal brand.//It’s true! Look it up in the library or something.

Text.SourceString: It looks small from the outside, doesn’t it?
Text.LocalizedString: It looks small from the outside, doesn’t it?

Text.SourceString: This is my favorite spot because I can gaze at the stars every night from my van.
Text.LocalizedString: This is my favorite spot because I can gaze at the stars every night from my van.

Text.SourceString: Walking is solid exercise. But it's also crucial to take a breather and mind your mental health.
Text.LocalizedString: Walking is solid exercise. But it's also crucial to take a breather and mind your mental health.

Text.SourceString: I was out foraging the other day, and I dozed off on the pier.//<portrait=angry>When <NpcName>Charles</> woke me up, I found myself at the clinic. Didn't recall a thing!//<portrait=annoyed>Still made me foot the bill, though.
Text.LocalizedString: I was out foraging the other day, and I dozed off on the pier.//<portrait=angry>When <NpcName>Charles</> woke me up, I found myself at the clinic. Didn't recall a thing!//<portrait=annoyed>Still made me foot the bill, though.

Text.SourceString: Lost money on that one. Oh well… I must have been really tired that day.//<portrait=sad>Or maybe I had too much…umm… Never mind.
Text.LocalizedString: Lost money on that one. Oh well… I must have been really tired that day.//<portrait=sad>Or maybe I had too much…umm… Never mind.

Text.SourceString: When the season shifts, your body oil shifts too. Told myself, “<NpcName>Ben</>, some days you’re a greaseball, and that's no fun. Time for a bath.” Then it clicked.//<portrait=angry>You know, <PlayerName>$player</>. Like yeah, this is a greasy day.
Text.LocalizedString: When the season shifts, your body oil shifts too. Told myself, “<NpcName>Ben</>, some days you’re a greaseball, and that's no fun. Time for a bath.” Then it clicked.//<portrait=angry>You know, <PlayerName>$player</>. Like yeah, this is a greasy day.

Text.SourceString: I went and took a bath. Submerged in my inner thoughts, cleansed myself. Then I foraged for dinner.
Text.LocalizedString: I went and took a bath. Submerged in my inner thoughts, cleansed myself. Then I foraged for dinner.

Text.SourceString: I wanted to spend the day petting ducks, but here I am…
Text.LocalizedString: I wanted to spend the day petting ducks, but here I am…

Text.SourceString: What should I have for dinner today?
Text.LocalizedString: What should I have for dinner today?

Text.SourceString: Your presence cleanses my aura right away, <PlayerName>$Player</>.//<portrait=normal>Powerful stuff.
Text.LocalizedString: Your presence cleanses my aura right away, <PlayerName>$Player</>.//<portrait=normal>Powerful stuff.

Text.SourceString: I had a dream last night about living on a cloud with rainbows as my roof.//It was so fluffy and colorful.
Text.LocalizedString: I had a dream last night about living on a cloud with rainbows as my roof.//It was so fluffy and colorful.

Text.SourceString: The dream was so real, I was surprised to wake up in my bed.//<portrait=blushing>You’d like the place, <PlayerName>$Player</>. Maybe we could live there together someday.
Text.LocalizedString: The dream was so real, I was surprised to wake up in my bed.//<portrait=blushing>You’d like the place, <PlayerName>$Player</>. Maybe we could live there together someday.

Text.SourceString: People look at me and think what they wanna think. The best advice I’ve ever gotten? Let them.//<portrait=normal>Because you can be the sweetest banana in the world, and there will always be somebody who doesn’t like bananas.
Text.LocalizedString: People look at me and think what they wanna think. The best advice I’ve ever gotten? Let them.//<portrait=normal>Because you can be the sweetest banana in the world, and there will always be somebody who doesn’t like bananas.

Text.SourceString: Keep being the good person that you are.//<portrait=annoyed>Now, do you know where I can get some bananas?
Text.LocalizedString: Keep being the good person that you are.//<portrait=annoyed>Now, do you know where I can get some bananas?

Text.SourceString: I don’t do those positivity things. I say we need to stay true to our feelings.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t do those positivity things. I say we need to stay true to our feelings.

Text.SourceString: <PlayerName>$Player</>, if I’m sad, you better believe you’ll see me sad.//<portrait=happy>There’s no point in telling folks to be happy when they’re sad. Let me be sad.//It’s okay to be sad.
Text.LocalizedString: <PlayerName>$Player</>, if I’m sad, you better believe you’ll see me sad.//<portrait=happy>There’s no point in telling folks to be happy when they’re sad. Let me be sad.//It’s okay to be sad.

Text.SourceString: Let your emotions out!
Text.LocalizedString: Let your emotions out!

Text.SourceString: When I’m alone in my caravan and all zoned out, I’m almost positive I can hear some sort of melody playing, but I don’t know where it’s coming from.//The mind-blowing part is I swear there are different songs for different seasons.
Text.LocalizedString: When I’m alone in my caravan and all zoned out, I’m almost positive I can hear some sort of melody playing, but I don’t know where it’s coming from.//The mind-blowing part is I swear there are different songs for different seasons.

Text.SourceString: I told people about it, but they said I needed to get some sleep.//<portrait=normal>They’re not wrong, but I know deep down that <Italic>I’m</> not wrong either.
Text.LocalizedString: I told people about it, but they said I needed to get some sleep.//<portrait=normal>They’re not wrong, but I know deep down that <Italic>I’m</> not wrong either.

Text.SourceString: Hang on! Did you hear that?
Text.LocalizedString: Hang on! Did you hear that?

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Suki</> is a beautiful soul. I feel like maybe she and I are on the same wavelength.//The platonic kind, though. Strictly friends.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Suki</> is a beautiful soul. I feel like maybe she and I are on the same wavelength.//The platonic kind, though. Strictly friends.

Text.SourceString: As for us, we're pretty tight, huh? But hey, I’m not hustling for anything in this universe, <PlayerName>$player</>.//Just a comfortable cruising altitude and a chance to ride the wave away…
Text.LocalizedString: As for us, we're pretty tight, huh? But hey, I’m not hustling for anything in this universe, <PlayerName>$player</>.//Just a comfortable cruising altitude and a chance to ride the wave away…

Text.SourceString: Ah, hot pepper jam. Coral island’s delicacy. Looks rather disgusting.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, hot pepper jam. Coral island’s delicacy. Looks rather disgusting.

Text.SourceString: Hold on… Did <Italic>you</> make this?
Text.LocalizedString: Hold on… Did <Italic>you</> make this?

Text.SourceString: I wanted to spend the day petting ducks. But here I am…//<portrait=annoyed>Who would have thought?
Text.LocalizedString: I wanted to spend the day petting ducks. But here I am…//<portrait=annoyed>Who would have thought?

Text.SourceString: Should I pay <NpcName>Suki</> a visit? I mean, she’s right there.
Text.LocalizedString: Should I pay <NpcName>Suki</> a visit? I mean, she’s right there.

Text.SourceString: What should I say?
Text.LocalizedString: What should I say?

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Suki</> is such a super lady. Ha ha ha… Umm…
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Suki</> is such a super lady. Ha ha ha… Umm…

Text.SourceString: It’s a slow day for me, my friend. I took a walk to the lake this morning and ended up here.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s a slow day for me, my friend. I took a walk to the lake this morning and ended up here.

Text.SourceString: What?
Text.LocalizedString: What?

Text.SourceString: I have a customer in the desert who's a huge fan of seashells.//<portrait=happy>Nah, mate. Just a customer. We aren’t that close.
Text.LocalizedString: I have a customer in the desert who's a huge fan of seashells.//<portrait=happy>Nah, mate. Just a customer. We aren’t that close.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes I think this is where I belong. The beach feels right to me…<Italic>and</> to my butt.//<portrait=blushing>It feels better to sit on the sand than on the lumpy ground in the forest.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes I think this is where I belong. The beach feels right to me…<Italic>and</> to my butt.//<portrait=blushing>It feels better to sit on the sand than on the lumpy ground in the forest.

Text.SourceString: You get things crawling out of the ground there.//It’s full of surprises.
Text.LocalizedString: You get things crawling out of the ground there.//It’s full of surprises.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Suki</> is super chill.//<portrait=normal>A wholesome type of lady and an incredible mom.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Suki</> is super chill.//<portrait=normal>A wholesome type of lady and an incredible mom.

Text.SourceString: She’s pretty good at mini golf too. Heh heh.
Text.LocalizedString: She’s pretty good at mini golf too. Heh heh.

Text.SourceString: Nah, mate. I don’t wander over there.//That part of the forest is too deep for me.
Text.LocalizedString: Nah, mate. I don’t wander over there.//That part of the forest is too deep for me.

Text.SourceString: I don’t touch nature where it doesn’t wanna be touched, you know what I mean? Let nature be.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t touch nature where it doesn’t wanna be touched, you know what I mean? Let nature be.

Text.SourceString: You’re so cute today, <PlayerName>$Player</>.
Text.LocalizedString: You’re so cute today, <PlayerName>$Player</>.

Text.SourceString: My face is all hot.
Text.LocalizedString: My face is all hot.

Text.SourceString: I’m gonna miss you when I’m gone on my trip.//<portrait=normal>Promise you won’t forget about me.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m gonna miss you when I’m gone on my trip.//<portrait=normal>Promise you won’t forget about me.

Text.SourceString: I thought about you when I was on the road, like <Italic>every</> day.//I missed you so much.
Text.LocalizedString: I thought about you when I was on the road, like <Italic>every</> day.//I missed you so much.

Text.SourceString: Gosh, you look good.
Text.LocalizedString: Gosh, you look good.

Text.SourceString: If you’re cold, we could go to the hot spring together.//<portrait=normal>It’ll help with umm…the coldness.
Text.LocalizedString: If you’re cold, we could go to the hot spring together.//<portrait=normal>It’ll help with umm…the coldness.

Text.SourceString: I haven’t even left, but I can’t wait to come back to you.
Text.LocalizedString: I haven’t even left, but I can’t wait to come back to you.

Text.SourceString: I’m afraid to bring Funbucket to town.//<portrait=annoyed>Don’t want him freaking out because of <NPCName>Taco</> or the cats.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m afraid to bring Funbucket to town.//<portrait=annoyed>Don’t want him freaking out because of <NPCName>Taco</> or the cats.

Text.SourceString: Funbucket gets scared easily. Poor lil fella.//Such a jumpy guy.
Text.LocalizedString: Funbucket gets scared easily. Poor lil fella.//Such a jumpy guy.

Text.SourceString: I wanna try dressing up like <NpcName>Dr. Charles</>. Just to see how it feels to be Sleek Style <NpcName>Ben</>.//<portrait=normal>He has a nice button-down on. Seems breezy, a nice green color.
Text.LocalizedString: I wanna try dressing up like <NpcName>Dr. Charles</>. Just to see how it feels to be Sleek Style <NpcName>Ben</>.//<portrait=normal>He has a nice button-down on. Seems breezy, a nice green color.

Text.SourceString: Eh, I don’t know. It doesn’t seem like me.//<portrait=annoyed>Long pants in Summer, yeah… I don’t know.
Text.LocalizedString: Eh, I don’t know. It doesn’t seem like me.//<portrait=annoyed>Long pants in Summer, yeah… I don’t know.

Text.SourceString: A lot of people have a great aura today.//I credit the sunny day.
Text.LocalizedString: A lot of people have a great aura today.//I credit the sunny day.

Text.SourceString: Taco often smells like <NpcName>Luke’s</> cologne.//Why, do you suppose?
Text.LocalizedString: Taco often smells like <NpcName>Luke’s</> cologne.//Why, do you suppose?

Text.SourceString: Oh yeah, <Italic>that’s</> why. Very funny!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh yeah, <Italic>that’s</> why. Very funny!

Text.SourceString: Yeah, <NpcName>Luke</> loves him so much.
Text.LocalizedString: Yeah, <NpcName>Luke</> loves him so much.

Text.SourceString: You think so too? I knew it!
Text.LocalizedString: You think so too? I knew it!

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Luke</> makes great food. He sends me jars of apple jam sometimes.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Luke</> makes great food. He sends me jars of apple jam sometimes.

Text.SourceString: It’s <Italic>great</> apple jam.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s <Italic>great</> apple jam.

Text.SourceString: The forest holds her own story, for sure…//I don’t bother her.
Text.LocalizedString: The forest holds her own story, for sure…//I don’t bother her.

Text.SourceString: I went to the lake yesterday. It was so peaceful and pretty.//<portrait=blushing>If I ever get married, I’d love to do it there. Surrounded by the beauty of nature, birds…friends.
Text.LocalizedString: I went to the lake yesterday. It was so peaceful and pretty.//<portrait=blushing>If I ever get married, I’d love to do it there. Surrounded by the beauty of nature, birds…friends.

Text.SourceString: I wouldn’t wear this, of course! I’d put on something <Italic>nice</>.
Text.LocalizedString: I wouldn’t wear this, of course! I’d put on something <Italic>nice</>.

Text.SourceString: You wouldn’t believe this shirt was once white. Very boring.//<portrait=annoyed>I, uh, I dyed it myself. It fits more with who I am now.
Text.LocalizedString: You wouldn’t believe this shirt was once white. Very boring.//<portrait=annoyed>I, uh, I dyed it myself. It fits more with who I am now.

Text.SourceString: Gotta wear shoes. The snow doesn’t vibe with sandals.// Gotta <Italic>love</> your toes.
Text.LocalizedString: Gotta wear shoes. The snow doesn’t vibe with sandals.// Gotta <Italic>love</> your toes.

Text.SourceString: Still no on the boots, though. Yeah, I don’t need boots.
Text.LocalizedString: Still no on the boots, though. Yeah, I don’t need boots.

Text.SourceString: My stove broke last week. It was a mess.//Good thing I have an electric skillet.
Text.LocalizedString: My stove broke last week. It was a mess.//Good thing I have an electric skillet.

Text.SourceString: I can’t get a better stove for the caravan. There isn’t space for one.//Anything better than the one I have would be too big.
Text.LocalizedString: I can’t get a better stove for the caravan. There isn’t space for one.//Anything better than the one I have would be too big.

Text.SourceString: I cooked some durian the other day. Yeah, you heard right. I <Italic>cooked</> it.//<portrait=concerned>It was bad.
Text.LocalizedString: I cooked some durian the other day. Yeah, you heard right. I <Italic>cooked</> it.//<portrait=concerned>It was bad.

Text.SourceString: The whole caravan smelled like wet socks.//<portrait=sad>I can still smell it. I think the smell is permanently lodged in my nose.
Text.LocalizedString: The whole caravan smelled like wet socks.//<portrait=sad>I can still smell it. I think the smell is permanently lodged in my nose.

Text.SourceString: Someone rear-ended my van on the way to Flower Valley.//I was stationary at a red light, and wham! Suddenly, got hit from behind
Text.LocalizedString: Someone rear-ended my van on the way to Flower Valley.//I was stationary at a red light, and wham! Suddenly, got hit from behind

Text.SourceString: Some stuff got knocked off the counter and shattered. Lost some crystals, and one of my cabinets got dinged, but luckily, no one was hurt.//<portrait=sad>My home was pretty wrecked. It made me sad to see it.
Text.LocalizedString: Some stuff got knocked off the counter and shattered. Lost some crystals, and one of my cabinets got dinged, but luckily, no one was hurt.//<portrait=sad>My home was pretty wrecked. It made me sad to see it.

Text.SourceString: One of the downsides of being on the road is the lack of showers.//Not every site has one.
Text.LocalizedString: One of the downsides of being on the road is the lack of showers.//Not every site has one.

Text.SourceString: I don’t consider myself homeless, because I have a home.//It’s just not a standard “house.”
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t consider myself homeless, because I have a home.//It’s just not a standard “house.”

Text.SourceString: Truth be told, a traditional house is far too expensive for me to afford.//<portrait=concerned>Even if I was down to settle, I don't think I could swing it.
Text.LocalizedString: Truth be told, a traditional house is far too expensive for me to afford.//<portrait=concerned>Even if I was down to settle, I don't think I could swing it.

Text.SourceString: The sound of the waterfall is super calming.
Text.LocalizedString: The sound of the waterfall is super calming.

Text.SourceString: I’ve never seen any of the town pets wandering around here. Not <NPCName>Taco</>, not <NPCName>Bonbon</>, not even the cats.
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve never seen any of the town pets wandering around here. Not <NPCName>Taco</>, not <NPCName>Bonbon</>, not even the cats.

Text.SourceString: Maybe the monkeys scare them away.
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe the monkeys scare them away.
